Class LogoutActionMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.struts.config.BaseConfig
      • org.apache.struts.config.ActionConfig
        • org.apache.struts.action.ActionMapping
          • com.mockrunner.example.struts.LogoutActionMapping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class LogoutActionMapping
extends org.apache.struts.action.ActionMapping
    This custom action mapping is used by LogoutAction to get the parameter name for the logout request parameter. The parameter name can be set in the struts-config.xml file using <set-property property="requestParameterName" value="logout"/>
